            <h1 class="font-migra text-4xl md:text-6xl lg:text-7xl font-bold mb-8 leading-tight">
                Your Story. Your Voice. Your Legacy — With Effortless Excellence.
            </h1>
            <p class="text-lg md:text-xl mb-10 leading-relaxed max-w-3xl mx-auto">
