                DISCOVER YOUR PODCAST PATH
            </a>
            <p class="text-sm text-brand-white/80">
                Ready to go now? <a href="#investment" class="underline hover:text-brand-peach transition-colors">Book Your Vision & Story Alignment Session</a>
            </p>
        </div>
    </section>

    <!-- Section 2: The Philosophy -->
    <section class="py-20 bg-brand-black">
        <div class="container mx-auto px-6 max-w-4xl">
            <h2 class="font-migra text-3xl md:text-5xl font-bold mb-12 text-center">
                In a World of AI-Generated Noise, Your Real Edge is Your Lived Story.
            </h2>
            <div class="space-y-6 text-lg md:text-xl">
                <p class="flex items-start">
                    <span class="text-brand-peach mr-3">•</span>
                    <span>Tech shouldn't block your message.</span>
                </p>
                <p class="flex items-start">
                    <span class="text-brand-peach mr-3">•</span>
                    <span>Your focus belongs in your genius.</span>
                </p>
                <p class="flex items-start">
                    <span class="text-brand-peach mr-3">•</span>
                    <span>"Where do I start?" shouldn't stop you.</span>
                </p>
            </div>
            <p class="text-xl md:text-2xl font-bold mt-12 text-center">
                Your voice deserves the highest care and attention.
            </p>
        </div>
    </section>

    <!-- Section 3: The Four Pillars -->
    <section class="py-20 bg-brand-black">
        <div class="container mx-auto px-6 max-w-6xl">
            <div class="grid grid-cols-1 md:grid-cols-2 lg:grid-cols-4 gap-8">
                <!-- Pillar 1 -->
                <div class="border border-brand-white/20 p-8 rounded-lg hover:border-brand-peach transition-colors">
                    <h3 class="font-migra text-2xl font-bold mb-4 text-brand-peach">1. Effortless Excellence</h3>
                    <p class="text-base">You speak; I handle the rest.</p>
                </div>
                <!-- Pillar 2 -->
                <div class="border border-brand-white/20 p-8 rounded-lg hover:border-brand-lime transition-colors">
                    <h3 class="font-migra text-2xl font-bold mb-4 text-brand-lime">2. Strategic Storytelling</h3>
                    <p class="text-base">Episodes that build toward your bigger goals.</p>
                </div>
