                    </div>
                </div>
                <div class="flex items-start">
                    <span class="font-migra text-3xl font-bold mr-6 flex-shrink-0">5.</span>
                    <div>
                        <h3 class="font-bold text-xl mb-2">Launch & Amplify</h3>
                        <p>Seamless hosting, distribution, and a tailored launch kit to ensure your message is heard.</p>
                    </div>
                </div>
            </div>
        </div>
