                    <span class="text-brand-white/50 mr-3">•</span>
                    <span>You're looking for a quick, one-off project.</span>
                </p>
                <p class="flex items-start">
                    <span class="text-brand-white/50 mr-3">•</span>
                    <span>You want to micro-manage.</span>
                </p>
                <p class="flex items-start">
                    <span class="text-brand-white/50 mr-3">•</span>
                    <span>You're happy to sacrifice quality.</span>
                </p>
